hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I came here to study how to apply clindamycin phosphate topical gel 1 I visited Sheardown (real name Gerald – Duffy is a nickname he picked up in secondary school) at his base in Cleethorpes, a stroll away from the seafront cafés selling belt-buster breakfasts and four doughnuts for £1. The factory – two small rooms on an industrial estate – is a far cry from the sleek, heavily branded super-plants I have visited on the Continent. There are some battered kitchen units, a couple of stainless steel tables, a pile of bowls from Poundland, and an intense, almost floral aroma of chocolate.
